plot: Reality program that spotlights the touching personal stories and saucy confessions of patrons, along with the sizzling celebrity exploits and the dramatic mounting tensions amongst the store's colorful staff, as the worlds first tattoo parlor inside a major Las Vegas casino resort opens its doors to the public.   Written by  Brahm Taylor
